### View your current credit balance (available, reserved, and total)
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View the full history of all your credit transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View your credit transaction history with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/credits/history?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

